comments: Herro (MIA) and Ingles (UTA) briefly engage on the perimeter as Herro, and Herro does not dislodge Ingles from his defensive position.
Gobert (UTA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Mitchell (UTA) makes marginal contact with Herro (MIA) at the start of his drive and Herro is able to maintain possession of the ball and continue his dribble.
Gobert (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Herro (MIA).
Herro (MIA) moves legally alongside of Mitchell (UTA) with his right arm collapsed against his body and he does not deliver contact to Mitchell during the drive.
O'Neale (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Dragic (MIA).
Herro (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Mitchell (UTA).
Adebayo (MIA) establishes a legal picking position as he is firmed up and does not deliver contact to O'Neale (UTA) during the pick.
O'Neale (UTA) jumps alongside of Butler (MIA) during the shot attempt and he does not make any contact with Butler.
Herro (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Ingles (UTA).
Ingles (UTA) makes marginal contact with Herro (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
As Herro (MIA) has gathered the ball and is beginning to pass, Ingles (UTA) legally swipes at the ball and does not make contact with Herro.
Adebayo (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Gobert (UTA).
Bogdanovic (UTA) commits a take foul on Robinson (MIA).
Gobert (UTA) is in a legal screening position as he firms up and does not deliver contact to Jones Jr. (MIA).  Jones Jr. moves into Gobert and initiates the contact.
Gobert (UTA) establishes a legal screening position as he is firmed up and does not deliver contact to Butler (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Mitchell (UTA).
Ingles (UTA) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Bogdanovic (UTA).
Dragic (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Gobert (UTA).
